metadata.description: Alice in NFT Space (AINS) is a collection of 5252 NFTs representing the visa needed to compete in The Game created by The Game Designer. Every minted visa represent a life for the holders and it will have different roles and traits that will be advantageous for The Game. Defeat the Game Designer to win it all. The Game Designer awaits you @ https://aliceinnft.space/.
